  "transcript": [
    {
      "id": "line-000",
      "start": 0.8,
      "end": 5.66,
      "text": "This is a LibriVox recording. All LibriVox recordings are in the public domain.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-001",
      "start": 6.92,
      "end": 11.52,
      "text": "For more information or to volunteer, please visit LibriVox.org.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-002",
      "start": 12.92,
      "end": 16.08,
      "text": "Asaps, Fables, the Wolf and the Crane.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-003",
      "start": 17.92,
      "end": 19.88,
      "text": "A Wolf once got a bone stuck in his throat.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 21.04,
      "end": 24.96,
      "text": "So he went to a crane and begged her to put her long bell down his throat and pull it out.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 26.3,
      "end": 28.02,
      "text": "I'll make it work your while he added.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 29.22,
      "end": 32.38,
      "text": "The Crane did as she was asked and got the bone out quite easily.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 33.78,
      "end": 37.28,
      "text": "The Wolf thanked her warmly and was just turning away when she cried.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 38.12,
      "end": 39.44,
      "text": "What about that feel-mine?",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 40.2,
      "end": 44.28,
      "text": "Well, what about it snapped the Wolf, bearing his feet as he spoke.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 45.3,
      "end": 50.26,
      "text": "You can go about boasting that you once put your head into a wolf's mouth and didn't get it bitten off.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 51.04,
      "end": 52.08,
      "text": "What more do you want?",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-012",
      "start": 55.68,
      "end": 57.12,
      "text": "End of the wolf and the crane.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
